<section class="visit-section">
  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Your First Visit</p>
      <h2>What to Expect</h2>
      <p>
        Visiting a church for the first time can feel uncertain. We want you to
        feel comfortable and welcomed before you ever walk through the doors.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="visit-grid">
      <article class="visit-card">
        <h3>Come as You Are</h3>
        <p>
          You do not need to dress a certain way. You will find people wearing
          everything from casual clothes to traditional Sunday attire.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="visit-card">
        <h3>Friendly Welcome</h3>
        <p>
          Our church family will be glad to meet you and help you find your way
          around without putting you on the spot.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="visit-card">
        <h3>Something for Children</h3>
        <p>
          Nursery care is available during all services, and Bible classes are
          available for children during Sunday School and Wednesday Bible Study.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="visit-card">
        <h3>Biblical Worship</h3>
        <p>
          Our worship services include music, prayer, fellowship, and practical
          preaching from the Bible.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="visit-callout">
      <div>
        <p class="section-eyebrow">Ready to Visit?</p>
        <h3>We would love to meet you this Sunday.</h3>
      </div>

      <a href="/visit" class="primary-button">Plan Your Visit</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>